# WordPress Admin Development Best Practices

## Admin Settings Pages
- Use `add_options_page()` for settings pages under Settings menu
- Use `add_menu_page()` for top-level admin pages
- Use `add_submenu_page()` for submenu pages
- Always check user capabilities with `current_user_can()`
- Use `register_setting()` to register settings
- Use `add_settings_section()` and `add_settings_field()` for form fields

## Settings API
- Use WordPress Settings API for all forms
- Register settings with `register_setting()`
- Use `settings_fields()` and `wp_nonce_field()` in forms
- Use `do_settings_sections()` to display sections
- Use `get_option()` and `update_option()` for data storage

## Admin Notices
- Use `admin_notices` hook for displaying notices
- Use `add_action('admin_notices', 'aamgr_admin_notice')`
- Use WordPress notice classes: `notice`, `notice-success`, `notice-warning`, `notice-error`, `notice-info`
- Use `is_admin()` to ensure notices only show in admin
- Use `wp_kses()` to sanitize notice content

## Admin UI Components
- Use WordPress admin styling classes
- Use `wp_enqueue_style()` for custom admin CSS
- Use `wp_enqueue_script()` for admin JavaScript
- Use WordPress color picker, date picker, and other UI components
- Follow WordPress admin design patterns

## Form Handling
- Always use nonces for form security
- Sanitize all form inputs
- Validate data before processing
- Use `wp_redirect()` for form redirects
- Display success/error messages using admin notices

## Capability Checks
- Use `current_user_can('manage_options')` for settings pages
- Use `current_user_can('edit_posts')` for content management
- Use `current_user_can('activate_plugins')` for plugin management
- Always check capabilities before displaying admin content
- Use `wp_die()` for unauthorized access

## Admin Hooks
- Use `admin_init` for admin initialization
- Use `admin_menu` for adding menu pages
- Use `admin_enqueue_scripts` for admin assets
- Use `admin_notices` for displaying notices
- Use `admin_footer` for admin footer content
